de.thkoeln.bibl.api.rfid.tag

Class ISO15693Tag

  • java.lang.Object
    • de.thkoeln.bibl.api.rfid.tag.BaseTag
      • de.thkoeln.bibl.api.rfid.tag.ISO15693Tag
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Comparable<BaseTag>
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    BibliothecaTag

    public class ISO15693Tag
extends BaseTag
    Class extends the base RFID tag with ISO 15693 features. Communication is based on the Feig IscTagHandler API. Instances of this class support XML serializing by JAXB. On object initialization all tag information and data will be read from the tag and stored for later offline access.
    Author:
    Patrick Rogalla

    Serialized Form
